Title: Exponential Hierarchy From Spacetime Variable String Vacua
Authors: P. Berglund, T. Hubsch and D. Minic
Comments: 22 pages, Latex, 2 figures
Journal-ref: JHEP 0009 (2000) 015
\\
  It is shown that non-supersymmetric spacetime varying string vacua can lead
to an exponential hierarchy between the electroweak and the gravitational
scales. The hierarchy is naturally generated by a string coupling of O(1).
